r: gold;\"><strong>你有頭盔同口罩可以當係環境証供</strong></span>之一，所以未必話到嗰個係你，但如果<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你搵個無police睇到既地掉左帽同除左口罩再融入人群，係更加好難指証你</strong></span>。<br />\n如果你無同police對抽，多數告你參與非法集結，而<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你如果有戴口罩，更加認唔到你，官冇可能係無合理疑點下話個個係你</strong></span>。&quot;"},{"pid":"7f66744e19b9f80b8fad538d987baf1ff961516a","tid":1318094,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"6bf9b97b1a065d118d55d203f50d2bc6337e32d2","tid":1318094,"uid":107663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}